.TH "RTCINBOUNDRTPSTREAMSTATS.FRAMESPERSECOND" "3JS" "August 15, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
RTCInboundRtpStreamStats.framesPerSecond \- RTCInboundRtpStreamStats:
framesPerSecond property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]framesPerSecond\f[B]\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]RTCInboundRtpStreamStats\f[R] dictionary indicates the number of
frames decoded in the last second.
.PP
Note that this may be lower than the media source frame rate, which is
provided in \f[CR]RTCVideoSourceStats.framesPerSecond\f[R].
.RS
.PP
\f[B]Note:\f[R] The value is undefined for audio streams.
.RE
.SH VALUE
A positive integer.
